<item>
            <title>[SOLR-662] support all highlighter parameters in solr-ruby</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-662</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;At present solr-ruby doesn&apos;t support the following hl functions:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;per-field override
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.snippets&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.fragsize&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.requireFieldMatch&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.simple.pre&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.simple.post&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;non-per-field-override
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.alternateField&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.maxAlternateFieldLength&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;other hl parameters
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.maxAnalyzedChars (w/ &lt;b&gt;per-field override&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.usePhraseHighlighter&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.mergeContiguous (w/ &lt;b&gt;per-field override&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.increment (w/ &lt;b&gt;per-field override&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.formatter (w/ &lt;b&gt;per-field override&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.fragmenter (w/ &lt;b&gt;per-field override&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.regex.slop (w/ &lt;b&gt;per-field override&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.regex.pattern (w/ &lt;b&gt;per-field override&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;hl.regex.maxAnalyzedChars (w/ &lt;b&gt;per-field override&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;A patch supports these functions will be shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
